===============================================================================
type-param-bound
===============================================================================
Trait with type parameter that has a trait bound.
Edge should be created from bound trait to the constrained trait.

--- file: sample/Cargo.toml ---
[package]
name = "sample"

--- file: sample/src/lib.rs ---
pub trait State {
    fn name(&self) -> &'static str;
}

pub trait Transition<To: State> {
    fn transition(self) -> To;
}

--- expect:block-graph ---
(root:1 001_lib (001_lib)
  (trait:2 State
    (method:3 name
      (parameter:4 self @type:2 State)
      (return:5 @type str)
    )
  )
  (trait:6 Transition
    (method:7 transition
      (parameter:8 self @type:6 Transition)
      (return:9 @type:2 State)
    )
  )
)

